## Description {#details}

Represents the stack and debug assignments in a block.

Used to describe the live-in and live-out values for blocks, as well as the &quot;current&quot; value as we process each instruction in a block.

Definition at line 1145 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp">AssignmentTrackingAnalysis.cpp</a>.

### LiveLoc {#a2093a4ceea2a878bc3123b23f27ca2f2}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>LocMap anonymous&#95;namespace&#123;AssignmentTrackingAnalysis.cpp&#125;::AssignmentTrackingLowering::BlockInfo::LiveLoc</>}>
Location kind for each variable.

LiveLoc indicates whether the dominating assignment in StackHomeValue (<a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp-/assignmenttrackinglowering/#a4012a71c02f4a13c5234aea48e772f4cadba5553473d129a7985fb532dc249ff4">LocKind::Mem</a>), DebugValue (<a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp-/assignmenttrackinglowering/#a4012a71c02f4a13c5234aea48e772f4ca5988c20a047cfe063999787584b0aca7">LocKind::Val</a>), or neither (<a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp-/assignmenttrackinglowering/#a4012a71c02f4a13c5234aea48e772f4ca6adf97f83acf6453d4a6a4b1070f3754">LocKind::None</a>) is valid, in that order of preference. This cannot be derived by inspecting DebugValue and StackHomeValue due to the fact that there&#39;s no distinction in <a href="/docs/api/structs/anonymous-namespace-assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp-/assignmenttrackinglowering/assignment">Assignment</a> (the class) between whether an assignment is unknown or a merge of multiple assignments (both are Status::NoneOrPhi). In other words, the memory location may well be valid while both DebugValue and StackHomeValue contain Assignments that have a <a href="/docs/api/structs/status">Status</a> of NoneOrPhi. Indexed by <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a8c9d5a3046b96979a032c218e858cd15">VariableID</a>.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp/#l01163">1163</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/assignmenttrackinganalysis-cpp">AssignmentTrackingAnalysis.cpp</a>.
</MemberDefinition>
